<view class="page-shell index-page">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <text class="hero-tag">CURRENT SEASON</text>
    <text class="hero-title">WoWLook</text>
    <text class="hero-copy">按职业、专精、副属性和部位筛选当前赛季掉落，直接查看副本、首领和装备说明。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="hero-stats">
    <view class="pill">{{overview ? overview.scope.dungeonCount : 0}} 个地下城</view>
    <view class="pill">{{overview ? overview.scope.raidCount : 0}} 个团本</view>
    <view class="pill">插件直连数据</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{overview}}" class="summary-card">
    <text class="summary-title">当前赛季快照</text>
    <text class="summary-copy">更新时间：{{overview.updatedAt}}</text>
    <text class="summary-copy">已跳过无英雄难度的世界首领集合，只保留正式团本。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <text class="section-title">选择职业</text>
    <text class="section-copy">先按职业进入，再按专精、副属性和部位继续筛选。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="class-grid">
    <view
      wx:for="{{classes}}"
      wx:key="id"
      class="class-card"
      bindtap="onClassTap"
      data-key="{{item.key}}"
      data-name="{{item.name}}"
    >
      <view class="class-mark" style="color: {{item.color}}; border-color: {{item.color}};">
        {{item.abbr}}
      </view>
      <text class="class-name" style="color: {{item.color}};">{{item.name}}</text>
      <text class="class-armor">{{item.armorTypeName}}</text>
      <text class="class-count">{{item.itemCount}} 件装备</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
